OL,6,FJurors were shown a video Richardson
OL,7,Fposted on Instagram of Meadowhall
OL,8,Fshopping centre, followed by a
OL,9,Fbrightly coloured clip featuring
OL,10,Fpictures of rainbows and dolphins,
OL,11,Foverlaid with the words: "How life
OL,12,Ffeels when you finally give up and
OL,13,Fjust start killing people brutally."
OL,15,FOther video clips included Richardson
OL,16,Fsmashing a statue of Buddha in a
OL,17,Fgarden, describing how it was a
OL,18,F"polytheistic idol", and also of him
OL,19,Ffiring a crossbow.
