OL,6,FHe told the trial his behaviour was a
OL,7,Fform of fantasy and escape from the
OL,8,Frest of his life, where he felt
OL,9,Fdepressed and isolated, and that he
OL,10,Fwas "role playing the character of an
OL,11,Fextremist".
OL,13,FBut prosecutors said he wasn't just an
OL,14,Fonline fantasist but an extremist who
OL,15,Fwas "going to put his jihadi fantasies
